    <h2 class="h2">What Treetop charges, specifically</h2>
    <p class="body">For comparison, here's how our productized engagements map to the table above:</p>
    <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;color:#C0D8C0;font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.85;">
      <li style="padding:0.5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;"><strong style="color:#F0FFF0;">$1,500</strong> — <a href="/services/ai-audit" style="color:#00C853;text-decoration:none;">AI Audit</a>: written roadmap only, no build</li>
      <li style="padding:0.5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;"><strong style="color:#F0FFF0;">$3,500+</strong> — <a href="/services/implementation" style="color:#00C853;text-decoration:none;">Implementation</a>: build the workflows, train the team</li>
      <li style="padding:0.5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;"><strong style="color:#F0FFF0;">$1,200/mo</strong> — <a href="/services/retainer" style="color:#00C853;text-decoration:none;">Monthly Retainer</a>: continuous optimization, new workflows, prompt maintenance</li>
      <li style="padding:0.5rem 0;"><strong style="color:#F0FFF0;">$5,000–$15,000/mo</strong> — Custom fractional engagements (CMO, CRO, AI Strategy) for larger companies needing executive-level AI leadership</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="body" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">Full pricing breakdown on the <a href="/pricing" style="color:#00C853;text-decoration:none;">pricing page</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

